headline: United Rentals (URI) Announces Dividend, Completed Buyback & Raises 2025 Revenue Guidance
summary: United Rentals (URI) recently reported its second-quarter results, showcasing an increase in sales and revenue but a slight decline in net income. The company also raised its full-year revenue guidance and declared a quarterly dividend. Furthermore, a completed share buyback program was announced. These developments appear to align with the positive market sentiment, as the company's stock price rose by 24% over the last quarter, significantly outpacing the broader market's 2% increase...
